OPEC basket price fell to $ 18 . 92 on Monday . The price of OPEC ' s basket of seven crudes stood at $ 18 . 92 per barrel on Monday , against $ 19 . 54 the previous Friday , according to the OPEC Secretariat ' s calculations , the OPEC news agency said on Thursday . The basket comprises Algeria ' s Saharan Blend , Indonesia ' s Minas , Nigeria ' s Bonny Light , Saudi Arabia ' s Arabian Light , Dubai of the UAE , Venezuela ' s Tia Juana and Mexico ' s Isthmus . - - London Newsroom + 44 171 542 7630 
